{"title":"ABAP: Sintaxe","uid":"7dfad76e64f44c07b3d1c07e4d7f0901","slug":"curso-abap-basico-02-sintaxe","date":"2022-11-02T03:49:22.729Z","updated":"2022-11-02T04:16:38.973Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/curso-abap-basico-02-sintaxe.json","keywords":["SAP","ABAP","Learn","Aprender","Software","Programação","Desenvolvimento","Desenvolvimento de Software"],"cover":"/img/default-cover.png","content":"<h3 id=\"Sintaxe-Basica\"><a href=\"#Sintaxe-Basica\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Sintaxe Básica\"></a>Sintaxe Básica</h3><p><code>&lt;PALAVRA-CHAVE&gt;</code> <code>&lt;ADITIVOS&gt;</code> <code>&lt;FIM INSTRUÇÃO&gt;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> hello <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Olá'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> world <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Mundo!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char1 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WRITE</span> hello <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> world<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Principais Caracteristicas de uma Instrução ABAP:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Declarações não possuem distinção entre maiusculas&#x2F;minusculas <em>Case Insesitive</em></li>\n<li>Normalmente começam com uma palavra chave <em>ABAP Keyword</em></li>\n<li>Devem possuir pelo menos um espaço entre palavras.</li>\n<li>Devem ser encerradas com um ponto <code>.</code> <em>End Statement</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Instrucoes-Encadeadas\"><a href=\"#Instrucoes-Encadeadas\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Instruções Encadeadas\"></a>Instruções Encadeadas</h3><p><code>&lt;PALAVRA-CHAVE&gt;</code> <code>&lt;OPERADOR&gt;</code><br>        <code>&lt;INSTRUÇÃO 1&gt;</code> <code>&lt;SEPARADOR&gt;</code><br>        <code>&lt;INSTRUÇÃO N&gt;</code> <code>&lt;SEPARADOR&gt;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    hello <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Olá'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    world <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Mundo!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char1 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WRITE</span> hello <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> world<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Instruções consecutivas podem ser combinadas através do operador de encadeamento após a palavra chave inicial <code>:</code> <em>Chain Operator</em> e separadas entre cada repetição por virgula <code>,</code> <em>Comma Separator</em></p>\n<p>Chamamos essa combinação de instruções encadeadas <em>Chained Statements</em></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Comentarios\"><a href=\"#Comentarios\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Comentários\"></a>Comentários</h3><p><code>*</code> <code>&quot;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Programa: RESERVAS</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Autor: ABAP Developer</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPORT</span> BOOKINGS<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* Recupera os dados das reservas de hospedagem do banco de dados</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> booking_info\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> accommodation_type <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'S'</span>          <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" Reservas em Suites</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> check_in_date     <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> sy_datum<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>    <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" A partir da data atual</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Comentarios podem ser declarados de duas formas: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Asterisco <code>*</code> como primeiro caractere de uma linha</li>\n<li>Aspas duplas <code>&quot;</code> em qualquer parte do código</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Qualquer declaração após estes caracteres, na mesma linha, serão consideradas comentários e não serão interpretadas pelo compilador</p>\n<br/>\n\n<p>Anterior: <a href=\"curso-abap-basico-01-abap\">ABAP</a><br>Próximo: <a href=\"curso-abap-basico-03-tipos-locais\">Tipos de Dados</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Sintaxe Básica&lt;PALAVRA-CHAVE&gt; &lt;ADITIVOS&gt; &lt;FIM INSTRUÇÃO&gt; CONSTANTS hello TYPE char5 VALUE 'Olá'. CONSTANTS world TYPE char...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ABAP","slug":"ABAP","count":3,"path":"api/categories/ABAP.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Curso ABAP","